      <h3 class="title"><a href="/blog/national-security-technology-and-liberty/beware-dangers-congress-latest-cybersecurity-bill" rel="bookmark" title="Beware the Dangers of Congress’ Latest Cybersecurity Bill">Beware the Dangers of Congress&rsquo; Latest Cybersecurity Bill</a></h3>
      <div class="metadata metadata-top clearfix">
        <div class="blogDate">06/27/2014</div>
        <div class="blogDateLine"><div class="social-links clearfix"><div class="item-list"><ul><li class="print first"><a href="/print/blog/national-security-technology-and-liberty/beware-dangers-congress-latest-cybersecurity-bill" target="_blank" title="Print this page">Print</a></li>
